
<ContentPage xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
             x:Class="comprehensure.DASHBOARD.StoryPage.StoryPage1"  
             BackgroundColor="#F4F8FB"
             Shell.NavBarIsVisible="False">


    <Grid RowDefinitions="Auto, *, Auto">

        <Border Grid.Row="0" BackgroundColor="#80c2ed" StrokeThickness="0" Margin="0,-10,0,0" HeightRequest="160">
            <Border.StrokeShape>
                <RoundRectangle CornerRadius="0,0,50,50" />
            </Border.StrokeShape>
            <VerticalStackLayout VerticalOptions="Center" Margin="0,10,0,0">
                <Label Text="The Forgotten Library" FontSize="28" FontAttributes="Bold" 
                       TextColor="#1B3A57" HorizontalOptions="Center" />
                <Label Text="Swipe to read the story" FontSize="14" TextColor="#1B3A57" 
                       HorizontalOptions="Center" Opacity="0.8"/>
            </VerticalStackLayout>
        </Border>

        <CarouselView Grid.Row="1" x:Name="StoryCarousel" Margin="0,20"
                      IndicatorView="indicatorView" PeekAreaInsets="30">
            <CarouselView.ItemsSource>
                <x:Array Type="{x:Type x:String}">
                    <x:String>In a quiet town surrounded by green hills, there stood an old library that most people had forgotten...</x:String>
                    <x:String>Inside, tall shelves were filled with dusty books. Some looked so old that their pages had turned yellow...</x:String>
                    <x:String>People in town often said that the library held forgotten knowledge, stories and letters...</x:String>
                    <x:String>One afternoon, a curious student named Leo decided to visit. Leo loved history...</x:String>
                    <x:String>While exploring the back corner of the library, Leo noticed something unusual. One bookshelf looked slightly out of place...</x:String>
                    <x:String>Leo carefully opened one journal. The writing inside was strange. It was written in shorthand...</x:String>
                    <x:String>For days after school, Leo returned to the library. He sat at the small desk and worked patiently...</x:String>
                    <x:String>One journal described an expedition where a group of travelers had disappeared...</x:String>
                    <x:String>History was not only about big events. It was about small details. It was about writing things down carefully...</x:String>
                    <x:String>After a month of hard work, Leo had translated several journals. He organized the information into clear notes...</x:String>
                    <x:String>The club decided to preserve the writings. Leo realized the most valuable knowledge is not always the most popular...</x:String>
                </x:Array>
            </CarouselView.ItemsSource>

            <CarouselView.ItemTemplate>
                <DataTemplate>
                    <Grid HorizontalOptions="Center" WidthRequest="700" VerticalOptions="Center">
                        <Border BackgroundColor="#BDE0FE" Rotation="-2" HeightRequest="450" TranslationY="8" StrokeThickness="0">
                            <Border.StrokeShape>
                                <RoundRectangle CornerRadius="30"/>
                            </Border.StrokeShape>
                        </Border>

                        <Border BackgroundColor="#FFF9C4" Padding="40" StrokeThickness="0" HeightRequest="450">
                            <Border.StrokeShape>
                                <RoundRectangle CornerRadius="30"/>
                            </Border.StrokeShape>
                            <Border.Shadow>
                                <Shadow Brush="#D4C463" Offset="0,10" Radius="20" Opacity="0.3"/>
                            </Border.Shadow>

                            <ScrollView>
                                <Label Text="{Binding .}" 
                                       FontSize="20" LineHeight="1.5" TextColor="#1B3A57" 
                                       HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" VerticalTextAlignment="Center" 
                                       FontFamily="Calibri" />
                            </ScrollView>
                        </Border>
                    </Grid>
                </DataTemplate>
            </CarouselView.ItemTemplate>
        </CarouselView>

        <VerticalStackLayout Grid.Row="2" Spacing="10" Padding="0,0,0,30">

            <HorizontalStackLayout HorizontalOptions="Center" Spacing="5" Margin="0,0,0,5">
                <Label Text="Slide " TextColor="Gray" FontSize="12" />
                <Label Text="{Binding Source={x:Reference StoryCarousel}, Path=Position}" 
                       TextColor="#1B3A57" FontAttributes="Bold" FontSize="12" />
                <Label Text=" of 11" TextColor="Gray" FontSize="12" />
            </HorizontalStackLayout>

            <IndicatorView x:Name="indicatorView"
                           IndicatorColor="#BDE0FE"
                           SelectedIndicatorColor="#1B3A57"
                           HorizontalOptions="Center" />

            <Button Text="GO TO QUIZ" 
                    BackgroundColor="#1B3A57" 
                    TextColor="White"
                    FontAttributes="Bold"
                    FontSize="18"
                    CornerRadius="30"
                    HeightRequest="60"
                    WidthRequest="250"
                    HorizontalOptions="Center"
                    Margin="0,10,0,0"
                    Clicked="OnGoToQuizClicked" />
        </VerticalStackLayout>
    </Grid>
</ContentPage>